    {
      "voiceId": "elizabeth-warren",
      "voiceName": "Elizabeth Warren",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "as Democrats we must resist the temptation of digital distractions on X (or whatever it\u2019s calling itself today) \ud83d\udcf1. Our time is best spent uniting against the tide of fascism \ud83e\uddb8\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\u270a, not squabbling over algorithms. Let\u2019s stay grounded, organized, and relentlessly committed to a better future #StayFocused",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/ewarren.bsky.social/post/3lb5iw5hovc2r",
      "timestamp": "2024-11-17T13:24:28.466Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "elizabeth-warren",
      "voiceName": "Elizabeth Warren",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "haha you would think that but its actually an honor \ud83e\udd70",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/ewarren.bsky.social/post/3lb5huzom5c2e",
      "timestamp": "2024-11-17T13:05:57.201Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "elizabeth-warren",
      "voiceName": "Elizabeth Warren",
      "platform": "bluesky",
      "text": "Trump & Musk\u2019s X are a threat to democracy & trans safety. \ud83d\udea8 Musk\u2019s free speech absolutism fuels hate, making transphobia mainstream. \ud83e\udde8 We can't let platforms amplify lies & harm. It's time to fight for a future where everyone is safe & heard. \ud83c\udf08\u270a  #DefendDemocracy  #TransLivesMatter #MuskIsDangerous",
      "sourceUrl": "https://bsky.app/profile/ewarren.bsky.social/post/3lb3wb4de322g",
      "timestamp": "2024-11-16T22:17:55.540Z",
      "type": "post"
    },
